\textbf{Hotel Results Summarizer}

\vspace{-1pt}

Built a tool using Python and LLM APIs to summarize hotel review data and surface top-rated properties per travel criteria.
\vspace{-1pt}
\begin{itemize}
\item Parsed and cleaned hotel review datasets using Python, Pandas, and RegEx before formatting into structured prompt-ready JSON.
\item Integrated OpenAI’s ChatGPT API to generate summarized hotel insights, weather highlights, and keyword breakdowns per region.
\item Deployed backend as a serverless function with AWS Lambda; results cached in DynamoDB for repeated regional lookup scenarios.
\item Designed frontend interface with React to allow instant user queries and display rating summaries using Chart.js visualizations.
\end{itemize}

